"{\"uid\": \"the42.ie-aidan-walsh-olympic-boxing-qualifier-6395073-May2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LAST UPDATE|31 May 2024  GR\\u00c1INNE WALSH WILL fight for Olympic qualification on Sunday morning after coming through\\u00a0her last-16 bout in the 66kg division in style on Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Aidan Walsh will have to win a four-man box-off this weekend to book his ticket to Paris after two point deductions cost him in the final Olympic\\u00a0qualification tournament in Bangkok.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 178, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.1578068126828092e-11, \"text\": \"Aidan Walsh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aidan_Walsh\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997339728, \"rank\": 2.661894739248305e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"score\": 0.9999998892271894, \"rank\": 5.6449471043870026e-08, \"text\": \"Bangkok\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bangkok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tokyo bronze medallist lost a 4-1 split decision to Jordanian Zeyad Eashash, which was decided by public warnings in the second and third rounds for\\u00a0excessive holding.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999976703293, \"rank\": 2.3281726929974664e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Belfast light middleweight's hopes of becoming a two-time Olympian now rest on the 71kg box-off, where he must win two bouts this weekend to secure the fifth and final qualification berth.\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 539, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"score\": 0.9999994699461735, \"rank\": 4.577579653451609e-07, \"text\": \"Belfast\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belfast\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999980768675716, \"rank\": 1.923136148090933e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walsh appeared well placed after a tactical first round saw him emerge on top of all five judges' scorecards.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The back-foot fighter was twice warned, however, by the Guatemalan referee over a lack of engagement.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That forced a change of approach as the second round wore on and once Eashash began to press forward, Walsh found himself in trouble.\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  He received a public warning for excessive holding but still did enough to tie the round 9-9\\u00a0with three judges (while the other two went 10-8 for\\u00a0Eashash) and held a narrow lead into the third.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Walsh continued to be spoken to by the referee and when he was again called for holding, it led to a public warning and another point docked.\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Being compelled to trade toe-to-toe favoured the Jordanian and he did enough, winning on all but one scorecard: 29-26, 29-26, 28-27, 28-27, 27-28.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Tullamore's Gr\\u00e1inne Walsh is just one win from making her Olympic debut after she earned a unanimous decision over\\u00a0Ivorian Sedia Sanogo in the 66kg last 16.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\", \"score\": 0.9999999999840838, \"rank\": 1.5843947552410152e-11, \"text\": \"Tullamore\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tullamore\"}, {\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gr\\u00e1inne_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.999999904902329, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gr\\u00e1inne Walsh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gr\\u00e1inne_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gr\\u00e1inne_Walsh\"}, {\"begin\": 1708, \"end\": 1715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999597333398016, \"rank\": 4.026818046141835e-05, \"text\": \"Ivorian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ivory_Coast_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Walsh returns to the ring on Sunday where she will face Armenia's Ani Hovsepyan to decide their Olympic fate.\", \"from\": 1751, \"to\": 1860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5972084107029042, \"rank\": 0.6744222110733897, \"text\": \"Armenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1817, \"end\": 1820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ani\", \"score\": 0.9926290473699052, \"rank\": 0.00742568701645718, \"text\": \"Ani\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ani\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier on Friday, Daina Moorehouse won her opening fight to progress to last 16 of the flyweight division.\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Enniskerry boxer received a split-decision win against Armenia's Anush Grigoryan, with a 4-1 majority from the judges.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enniskerry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Enniskerry\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enniskerry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Enniskerry\"}, {\"begin\": 2030, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5972084107029042, \"rank\": 0.6744222110733897, \"text\": \"Armenia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armenia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2040, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anush_(Mandaeism)\", \"score\": 0.5487804862215137, \"rank\": 0.8222222222224, \"text\": \"Anush\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anush_(Mandaeism)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anush_(Mandaeism)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took the first round on all but one of the scorecards before convincing all five in the second.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From there, it was a matter of holding her advantage to the finish.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Moorehouse needs two more victories to secure her Olympic qualification and will box again on Saturday.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, former world and European champion for Ireland Amy Broadhurst has fallen short in her bid to qualify for Team GB.\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2399, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Curling_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9210030697940621, \"rank\": 0.07371399570666384, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Curling_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Curling_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9988051565379755, \"rank\": 0.0011947232569306432, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2429, \"end\": 2443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"score\": 0.999994937526562, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amy Broadhurst\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amy_Broadhurst\"}, {\"begin\": 2487, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999975748324, \"rank\": 1.5827057064350852e-09, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dundalk lightweight switched allegiance after she was not selected for this Olympic qualifier by the IABA.\", \"from\": 2497, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [{\